parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column lock can cause the steering wheel to lock up, making it difficult or impossible to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The steering wheel locks up
the service steering column lock warning light illuminates
the vehicle stalls or loses power
and the airbag system may not deploy in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the vehicle to lose power steering assist, making it difficult to steer, especially at low speeds, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The power steering system fails
the steering becomes heavy or difficult to turn
and the vehicle may stall or lose power.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The service column lock warning indicator illuminates
the vehicle stalls without warning
the speedometer sticks or malfunctions
the dashboard lights darken or fail
the anti-theft system malfunctions
and the battery drains excessively.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The service ignition switch warning light illuminates
the vehicle stalls without warning
and the engine suddenly stops running.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the instrument panel can cause the driver to lose vital information, such as speed, leading to accidents or traffic violations.
symptoms: The speedometer sticks or malfunctions
the dashboard lights darken or fail
and the odometer fails to display correctly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the anti-theft system can cause the vehicle to malfunction or become inoperable, leading to inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The anti-theft system malfunctions
the vehicle fails to start
and the theft system light on the dashboard illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlights can cause reduced visibility, leading to accidents or safety risks.
symptoms: One or both headlights fail to function properly.
